description:
UPDATE:

I made a new version with a larger dataset, It's still not really where I want it to be but I'll keep working on it. As always happy generating!

Also please don't reupload my models, someone posted a couple of them on moescape and I can't claim them or anything. I'm doing this all out of my pocket and I mostly make my own images and it takes a lot of time so every bit of support helps.

This model produces a mix of dark fantasy and 90s and early 2000s anime style but made to have clean lines like modern anime.

I made another spinoff of this model with a different style you can find it here:https://civitai.com/models/827126/neonfantasynocturne-style-ponyxl

If you want to support me financially or request a custom LoRa you can do so here: KoFi

PonyXL

Usage:

Trigger word: ne0nfant4sy

Strength: I use 1 but feel free to experiment.

I recommend using Prefect Pony XL v3, T-ponynai3 and Base PonyXL

FLUX

Usage:

Trigger word: ne0nfant4sy

Strength: I found that 0.8 works best in my testings but feel free to experiment 1 is also good but maybe a bit less stable.

You can use PonyXL prompting as well as the usual FLUX prompting.
